識得利用便衣狗去幫我地達成目的。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><em>情況一（ 手足人數 &gt;&gt; 狗數量 ）：</em></strong></ins><br />\n呢個情況之下，基本上你走去目標商店鳩企，或者喺個商場唱歌漫步叫口號已經可以達到目標。由於有足夠嘅人數掩護，我極度<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔</span>建議勇武手足進場進行翻新工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為咁樣你地就好易成功離開，唔能夠將你地繩之於法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，如果夠人數的話基本上連裝修都唔需要就已經癱瘓咗個商場，風險亦都相對地低。呢個風險前線自己一定識衡量，點做都唔割蓆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>情況二 （ 手足人數 ＝ 狗數量 ）：</ins></em></strong><br />\n呢個情況就要引班便衣狗露出真面目，釀成言語上嘅衝突，好似今日新港城咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係嘅，同班便衣狗一齊和理Shop，鳩行鳩企鳩叫，利用假狗壯大自己人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候，勇武手足又可以化身為平民手足，因為出手嘅時機實在太不利，送命機會實在太高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>情況三 （ 手足人數 &lt;&lt; 狗數量 ）：</ins></em></strong><br />\n轉場啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家一定留意到防暴係最後個moment先會入嚟，因為佢一入嚟基本上成個商場都會即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毫無疑問地引防暴入場係最有效達到和理shop嘅目標，但自己始終極唔建議，因為真係唔想見到手足被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家識得按情況決定，唔使吓吓都話裝修，最緊要衡量咗風險先做，癱瘓商場唔一定要提高自身可以承受嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">安全至上</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be886795d7f0700f767648ee8beb0ef81bf537c1","tid":1792030,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"b6c996e4a2569dabe21aa53058f10419cad9d898","tid":1792030,"uid":51621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"參考下隔離個post<br />\n和你shop x 和你影<br />\n一路行一路影住班行街既港豬"},{"pid":"8c5a6c1a1c72c178e3effe2a08df4f9d0285cdb3","tid":1792030,"uid":114937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc897ec405bf9e717ab60b1bf2d7489211bb8e0a","tid":1792030,"uid":328812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f18c59b2b6d091ae5092819851168906615ea74","tid":1792030,"uid":328812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d73e4ee3eeb87caeaa2b665ddcf6ad62defde8","tid":1792030,"uid":149021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"真係好難知夠唔夠手足 便衣有幾多人 2/3都難判斷<br />\n大家都冇上帝視角 便衣又唔會額頭寫住個狗字<br />\n顯眼就易估 有d呀叔呀嬸估唔到"},{"pid":"d152d3ac304532d9a933709e57531be675fe7219","tid":1792030,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e183ce269c046f6be22bfdcf2b183c9242c0f47","tid":1792030,"uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"手足小心<br />\n就係要佢收皮 裝修 尻叫都係不同手段 但尻叫就減低被捕風險<br />\n<br />\n點都好 唔割 但手足小心"},{"pid":"1a1cb8c9add31f402dd32537dc26feabb032fefa","tid":1792030,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b2cdda2558782236a950e246b8d34b8ea1a3fbf6","tid":1792030,"uid":225818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"其實只要引到狗入場<br />\n商場舖頭關門<br />\n就可以閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a3c3121b937bce9383db7ec24e50c86a788f68","tid":1792030,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f7c512d32fee165fcb9c8c5c677556ca7d37b2","tid":1792030,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cd22fa12b7ac45491fa3baac04d86997171f0f","tid":1792030,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb54a7ab4e2f3a579272f27327da066e568cf3b","tid":1792030,"uid":51621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"要小心既係<br />\n你搵到=黑警搵到<br />\n要記住be water<br />\n小心為上"},{"pid":"34364720603f97b311a6b633ed6e4c5c93d02e2d","tid":1792030,"uid":272726,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"終於有啲取平衡嘅post，唔係淨係講勇武vs唔勇武，將討論兩極化。<br />\n而且另一重點係，就算勇武喺行動時機掌握得唔完美，都唔割。<br />\n<br />\n如果其他方法都有呢種心態就好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cba2053aed5de91e17f0c5ae63855a7b13e525","tid":1792030,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n1222聲援維吾爾族集會<br />\n已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n1530 - 1830<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgqPts5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgqPts5.png&h=bbe5e113&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21107aefa7c9475961c7c449884a3498a1d108cf","tid":1792030,"uid":254032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ddbf9e586ac652a266d8f7c83bd6999432bd5b6","tid":1792030,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"6afe7386aa9474d2bcab83135d356837f11e9b81","tid":1792030,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"c7d4